definitions.definition: An indigenous native islander of the Mariana Islands consisting of Guam and Northern Mariana Islands of Saipan , Rota , and Tinian .

main_definition: An indigenous native islander of the Mariana Islands consisting of Guam and Northern Mariana Islands of Saipan , Rota , and Tinian .

definitions.definition: An Austronesian language spoken by the indigenous native islanders of the Northern Mariana Islands and Guam.

main_definition: An Austronesian language spoken by the indigenous native islanders of the Northern Mariana Islands and Guam.
